             <p class="text-left"><strong>SSH Key Tool</strong>: generate new SSH keys for all nodes.<br />
              <strong>Configure IP Tool</strong>: configure a static IP and unique hostname for nodes.<br />
              <strong>Update Tool</strong>: remotely update all packages for the nodes.<br />
              <strong>Nodes File</strong>: file to hold all configured nodes.<br />
              <strong>Base Net</strong>: wireless access point running on boot, removing need for monitor.<br /></p>
